name: UndoModes
shortdesc: Undo options for executing a script.

property.name: SCRIPT_REQUEST
property.shortdesc: Undo each script request as a separate step.

property.name: ENTIRE_SCRIPT
property.shortdesc: Undo the entire script as a single step.

property.name: AUTO_UNDO
property.shortdesc: Automatically undo the entire script as part of the previous step.

property.name: FAST_ENTIRE_SCRIPT
property.shortdesc: Fast undo the entire script as a single step.
